# AmpliFinder Project Rules

# Python environment
- Use conda Python: /zdata/user-data/rkishony/.conda/envs/amplifinder/bin/python
- For pip: /zdata/user-data/rkishony/.conda/envs/amplifinder/bin/pip
- Always prefix python commands with the full path above

# Code style
- Short answers with code, no verbose explanations

# Conda activation
- No base conda on PATH; use env binaries directly.
- Preferred: export PATH="/zdata/user-data/rkishony/.conda/envs/amplifinder/bin:$PATH" then run tools.
- Or call full interpreter: /zdata/user-data/rkishony/.conda/envs/amplifinder/bin/python

